## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Claim a WU
pnpm wu:claim --id WU-XXXX --lane <Lane>
cd worktrees/<lane>-wu-xxxx

# 2. Work in worktree, run gates
pnpm gates

# 3. Complete (ALWAYS run this!)
cd {{PROJECT_ROOT}}
pnpm wu:done --id WU-XXXX
```

